✅ 分析结果

📊 04_Results/tree_cylinders.csv
   - 61 棵树的数据
   - 包含: 半径、胸径(DBH)、高度、点数
   
🗂️ 04_Results/tree_Off-ground points.section_RANSAC_DETECTED_SHAPES.bin
   - CloudCompare 格式的检测结果

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

✅ 技术栈

软件工具:
  - CloudCompare (点云预处理)
  - Python 3.11 (通过 conda)
  - conda (环境管理)

Python 库:
  - open3d (点云处理)
  - numpy (数值计算)
  - scipy (科学计算)
  - scikit-learn (PCA 算法)

算法:
  - RANSAC (随机采样一致性)
  - PCA (主成分分析)
  - 自定义圆柱体拟合

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

✅ 使用说明

日常运行:
  cd /Users/zyc/Downloads/Niigata_Research_Prep
  ./run_tree_detection.sh

参数调整:
  编辑 03_Scripts/detect_cylinders_v2.py
  调整 DISTANCE_THRESHOLD, MIN_RADIUS, MAX_RADIUS 等参数

查看文档:
  - 快速开始: cat QUICKSTART.md
  - 完整手册: open README.md
  - 操作总结: open OPERATION_SUMMARY.md

